The current profile text looks unappealing. To change this I thought of the following solution:

!suggestion.png!

h5. Instructions

# Add "profile-text" to the profile text "p" element
# Add the following CSS to AAC:

{code}
.profile-text {
	position:relative;
	padding:15px;
	margin:2em 0 3em;
	border:3px solid #C8DAEB;
	color:#333;
	background:#fff;
	-webkit-border-radius:10px;
	-moz-border-radius:10px;
	border-radius:10px;
}

.profile-text:before {
	content:"";
	position:absolute;
	border-style:solid;
    border-color:#C8DAEB transparent;
    display:block; 
    width:0;
    top:-20px; 
	bottom:auto;
	left:50px;
	right:auto;
    border-width:0 20px 20px;
}

.profile-text:after {
	content:"";
	position:absolute;
	border-style:solid;
	border-color:#fff transparent;
    display:block; 
    width:0;
    top:-13px;
	bottom:auto;
	left:57px;
	right:auto;
    border-width:0 13px 13px;
}
{code}

